"Alpha Mini" APP is a supporting application for UBTECH Mini Robot. Alpha Mini is an intelligent humanoid robot produced by the company UBTECH. It provides a plenty of functions for education and entertainment purposes, including photo taking, programming and dancing, etc. This APP can help manage your robot:



1. Control and use some functions of the robot;

2. Use graphical programming tools to learn about robot programming;

3. Understand the way to control and use the robot;

4. View and set up the configuration and information of the robot.

Aelos1S is the App to apply for mobile device's terminal control. 

Aelos1S App connect with Aelos1S robot via Bluetooth. Based on the mobile phone's APP, below function can be accomplished: 
- Download&play the music, fair tale, yoga in the Action store; 
- Keep the robot movement, play foot, boxing via remote controller; 
- DIY the action by programming of App, further share the new action to the action store. Let more people enjoy together;
- Check the battery volume,voice volume and other robot info; 
- Setup the wifi connectivity and make voice interaction with robot
- Robot firmware update.
